# Test: web auth -- valid auth returns content, missing auth returns login page
# VALIDATES: authentication middleware protects routes, login page served for unauthenticated
# PREVENTS: auth bypass or missing login redirect
#
# Placeholder: the .ci test runner does not yet support HTTPS clients.
# Full coverage is in internal/component/web/integration_test.go.
# This file exists for spec audit hooks. When the test runner gains
# HTTPS support, replace this with a real auth + request test.

cmd=foreground:seq=1:exec=ze web --help
expect=exit:code=0
expect=stderr:contains=ze web
